src:
Partizan vodi 2:0, Natho dvostruki srelac [VIDEO]
02 Nov 2019, 14:50 by Milos
Na stadionu u Humskoj u toku je utakmica 15. kola Linglong Super lige Srbije između Partizana i Vojvodine.
Crno-beli nakon prvog poluvremena vode sa 2:0, pogocima Bibrasa Natha iz jedanaesterca u 29. i 43. minutu.
Sudija Đorđić, koji je bio blizu mesta događaja je duel Devetka i Ostojića okarakterisao kao prekršaj i jedanaesterac, a Bibras Natho je bio siguran sa bele tačke.



Izraelac je drugi gol postigao nakon povratne lopte Sadika.




POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
Partizan leads 2: 0, Natho double meets [VIDEO]
02 Nov 2019, 14:50 by Milos
The 15th round of the Linglong Super League of Serbia between Partizan and Vojvodina is underway at the stadium in Humska.
Black and whites after the first half lead with 2-0 lead by Bibras Nath in the 29th and 43rd minutes.
Judge Djordjic, who was close to the scene, described the duel of Devetko and Ostojic as a foul and a penalty, and Bibras Natho was safe from a white spot.



The Israeli scored the second goal after Sadik's return ball.
